### use arandr to set screen preference
### save as ~/.screenlayout/dual-head.sh
### uncomment next line
# ~/.screenlayout/dual-head.sh

### activate natural scrolling
xinput set-prop 12 288 1 

### restore wallpaper
sleep 1; tint2 &

### enable numlock
### uncomment next line
#sleep 0.5; numlockx &

### sets the wallpaper
feh ~/.config/wallpaper/wallpaper.jpg --bg-scale

### start redshift settings for uk
redshift -l 50:1 &

### sets keyboard in english us
setxkbmap us 

